"29:38:12" : {s: 29, a: 38, w: 12, r: "صدد", t: "فَصَدَّهُمْ", l: "صَدَّ", lc: 37, tl: "faṣaddahum", lb: "বাঁধা দেয়",e: "and averted them", b: "", i: "lalu ia menghalangi mereka", f: 2, rm: "to turn away, divert, hinder, avert. sadiidan - to shun a thing, shrink from, raise, clamour, shout, cry aloud. saddun - the act of hindering, diverting or turning away. sadiid - anything that is repulsive, hot or boiling water.", ag: "فاء عطف وفعل ماض وضمير متصل ", eg: "Conjunctive fa and Verb Perfect and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "PERF", qual: "", deg: "3", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "", lu: "صَدَّ"},
